Scenario: Login test di website
Given User telah memasukkan username dan password
When User mengklik tombol "masuk"
Then Sistem akan melakukan validasi username dan password
And Sistem akan menampilkan halaman utama jika login berhasil
And Sistem akan menampilkan pesan error jika login gagal


Scenario: User registers on website
Given a user is on the website’s registration page
When they enter their username, password, email address and other required information and click the “Submit” button 
Then the website will validate that the information is correct and valid
And the user will be registered and be able to access the website’s services


Scenario: Login berhasil

Given User memasukkan username dan password
When User menekan tombol "Login"
Then User berhasil login dan dapat mengakses halaman Home


Scenario: Login gagal

Given User memasukkan username dan password yang salah
When User menekan tombol "Login"
Then User gagal login dan tidak dapat mengakses halaman Home